
Layout Classes:
.container: Centers and provides responsive padding.
.container-fluid: Full-width container, spanning the entire width of the viewport.
.row: Creates a horizontal group of columns.
.col: Automatically sizes columns for equal-width columns.
.col-{size}-{breakpoint}: Creates responsive columns (e.g., col-md-6).
.d-{value}: Display utilities (d-block, d-flex, d-none, etc.).
.justify-content-{value}: Justifies flexbox items (e.g., justify-content-center).
.align-items-{value}: Aligns flexbox items (e.g., align-items-start).

Typography Classes:
.text-left, .text-center, .text-right: Text alignment.
.text-muted: Muted/greyed-out text.
.font-weight-{value}: Set font weight (e.g., font-weight-bold).
.lead: Highlights introductory text with larger size and spacing.
.h1, .h2, .h3, .h4, .h5, .h6: Heading styles.

Spacing Classes:
.m-{side}-{value}: Margin utilities (e.g., m-3, mt-2, mr-1, etc.).
.p-{side}-{value}: Padding utilities (e.g., p-4, pb-2, etc.).

Button Classes:
.btn: Base button class.
.btn-primary, .btn-secondary, .btn-success, .btn-danger: Button color styles.
.btn-lg, .btn-sm: Button size.

Utility Classes:
.bg-{color}: Background color (e.g., bg-primary, bg-light).
.border: Adds a border around an element.
.rounded: Adds border-radius.
.shadow-sm, .shadow-lg: Shadow effects.